Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:14.79,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隠してた感情が　悲鳴を上げている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:14.79,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏起来的感情在呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.81,0:01:20.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確かな誓いを手に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.81,0:01:20.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手中紧握坚定的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:35.87,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡だけを求め
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:35.87,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想乞求一个奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:41.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消えない闇を彷徨う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:41.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨在消失不尽的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:46.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここに入れば　二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:46.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:51.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来見ることできない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:51.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前又将失去未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:54.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今宵も月が誘うって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:54.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今宵也有月来相邀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだ言葉出さないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说的话仍未传达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:01.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心の中叫び続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:01.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却在心中不停的回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:07.19,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隠してた感情が　悲鳴を上げている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:07.19,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏起来的感情在呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:12.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確かな誓いを手に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:12.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手中紧握坚定的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:17.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後ほんの少しだけ強くなれてなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:17.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再稍微坚强一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:21.67,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何の前にある この空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:21.67,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论前方将要面对什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:24.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超えて行くから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:24.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从超越这片天空开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:29.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この先にある未来に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:29.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着前方的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:32.77,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手を伸ばすから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:32.77,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 来的真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这店还是这么的不景气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话真多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上可是很热闹的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 那个照片 是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来话长了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 你知道么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「AmuSphere」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「NERvGear」后继机型对应的MMO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 它和SAO一样是VRMMO么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}VRMMO：大型虚拟网络游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.89,0:00:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ALfheim Online
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:00:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎发音为ALfheim
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是妖精的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\c&HE1BE56&\3c&H080808&\bord1\pos(517,458)\be2}妖精们的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精的国家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是休闲类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 好像不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全技巧制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重视玩家技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推荐PK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全技巧制？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说没有等级存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种技巧通过反复使用就能增强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗也依存于玩家的运动能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是没有剑技 而是使用魔法的SAO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个现在可是很有人气的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由就是 可以飞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以飞？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是妖精 所以是有翅膀的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它上面搭载了飞行引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟练掌握后就可以自由的飞行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要怎么控制呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过貌似很困难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是要操纵人类并不存在的翅膀嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是用背后的肌肉来操作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 这个大人气的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟亚丝娜有什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像… 亚丝娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然也这么认为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是在哪拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏里面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ALfheim Online」里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个似乎叫做 世界树
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这棵树的上面有一个传说中的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩家被分成9个不同的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相比拼着 看哪个种族能第一个到达城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞上去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像因为有什么滞空时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能一直飞在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是这时 出现了5个玩家按体型顺序叠罗汉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用多段火箭式方法飞了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然样子很蠢 但想法还不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样 他们也只到达了世界树最下端的树枝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们拍了几张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一张 出现了个稀奇的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟笼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个鸟笼的解像度放大到极限后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么亚丝娜会在这个游戏里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「RCT」出品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 明日奈生命是由我在维持着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾基尔 这个游戏能给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是可以 你要去么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要亲眼去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了可以复活的游戏 简直是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去买硬件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「NERvGear」就可以运行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「AmuSphere」只是「NERvGear」的安全强化版而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒是方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把亚丝娜救出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样的话 我们的战斗是不会结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 总有一天要在这里开线下通关庆功会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我还以为会死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个慌里慌张的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢点吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小直 关于昨晚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了小直 我又重新打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会把明日奈夺回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想见见明日奈姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一定会相处得很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 等会见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚仪式在一周后的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1月26日于这个病房举行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会请你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次 借给我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Link Start
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到AlFheim Online
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 请输入人物的性别及姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你就是那位英雄桐人君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(桐人 男)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 请选择您的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请从九个种族中选择一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您选择了守卫精灵「spriggan」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色外貌将随机生成 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在 您将被传送到守卫精灵的主城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您好运
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又发生什么事啦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:56.78,biaoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\blur3\pos(510,461)}ALFheim·中立区域·古森
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来到这里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明碰上过那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:35.63,biaoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(373,282)\frz6.953\3c&HF5EBDA&\c&HA29084&\shad0\fad(300,0)}在野外无法立刻下线 确认选择吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 看看人物状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}种族 守卫精灵 生命力 400 魔力   800 技能 单手剑 1000
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事 出BUG了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 这和SAO时的参数相同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在SAO里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:07.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,323)\c&HFDFEFF&\3c&H14AEF5&\shad0}道具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了… 一定要有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 又见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了吧 我们吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹发生了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这究竟是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是 这里并不是SAO的世界呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是个叫做「ALfheim Online」的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的游戏世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界 是SAO服务器的拷贝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拷贝？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本程序和图像形式是和SAO完全相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 主系统的版本稍微旧了点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运营SAO的ARGUS的事后处理 都被委托给了RCT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RCT吸收了ARGUS的技术资产 并将它挪用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么我的个人数据还被保留着呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 让我看一下爸爸的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有错呢 这就是爸爸在SAO里使用过的角色数据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这两个世界里的存档资料格式基本相同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以两个世界共通的技能熟练度才会被继承吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.38,0:14:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 二刀流技能不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道具也… 好像都损坏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被勘误程序检测出来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是赶紧扔掉比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HF5EBDA&\c&HA29084&\shad0\fad(0,0)\pos(603,86)\frz2.758}提示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:27.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA29084&\shad0\fad(300,0)\frz2.564\pos(531,296)\3c&HEFE3DA&}要删除全部道具吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 技能熟练度怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于技能 只要不是人工GM亲自确认
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就应该没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这… 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子已经不是封闭者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是纯粹的作弊者了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结衣 在这个世界里是什么身份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 辅助玩家的模拟人格程序
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被划分到「导航精灵」这类里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是我作为「导航精灵」的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你还和以前一样有管理员权限吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 现在能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有查询和连接广域地图数据而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里… 亚丝娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的妈妈好像在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 妈妈在？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚丝娜在SAO通关之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有回到现实世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说在ALfheim里有人看到过和亚丝娜很像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经知道她大概在哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个叫做「世界树」的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会在这种毫无人烟的森林里登录啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是被传送到主城镇才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚…可能是因为位置情报损坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是因为混线了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其掉在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如让我掉在世界树附近的好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是翅膀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样才能飞起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有辅助控制杆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出左手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出握住东西的姿势试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 向里拉是上升
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:16:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向下压是下降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右是旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按下按钮是加速 松开则是减速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀发光的这段时间是可以飞行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过一段时间之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须让翅膀休息才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.81,0:17:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 我大致明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 距离这里最近的城镇在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西边有一个属于风精灵「sylphid」的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做司伊鲁班的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是离这最近的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有玩家就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉… 莉法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊雷根
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样一路逃到风精灵的领地的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷根 快避开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真够烦人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 打不赢的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是西格鲁特他们 肯定也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽量多拖住几个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你至少得想办法打落一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会挂彩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也要让我看到你帅气的一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 别停下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷根
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这是我们的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把钱和道具留下的话 就放你一马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装哪门子的绅士啊 影宗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有女人当对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆杀了她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算死我也绝对要再拉一个人陪葬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕死亡惩罚的人就放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个倔强的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是着陆失误了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还愣着做什么 快点逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个重战士袭击一个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不太光彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你算哪根葱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新手也敢大摇大摆的出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你所愿 送你归西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什……！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这些人可以砍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应… 应该是没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少对方是这么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就失礼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来该轮到谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 被囚禁的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
